|---|---|---|
| **Security Headers** | None set | Added `helmet()` middleware |
| **Rate Limiting** | No protection against abuse | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **Input Validation** | No validation on query params | Added `express-validator` with whitelist checks |
| **Body Parsing** | No body parser configured | Added `express.json()` with `10kb` size limit |
| **Error Handling** | No global error handler | Added 404 handler + centralized error middleware |
| **Data Exposure** | Emails returned without auth | Removed PII from unauthenticated response |
| **Stack Trace Leak** | Default Express behavior exposes internals | Error handler returns generic message only |
